<item>
            <title>[LU-12917] Provide an official Lustre tarball</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12917</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Traditionally, open source software are distributed thanks to compressed tarball and optionally with some binary packages.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The packages used the official tarball as source of truth.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For some reason, no tarball is available on downloads.whamcloud.com and it could be interesting to provide one along with the various distribution packages, instead of relying on git clone + autogen.sh to get a working source tree.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This will make installation instruction easier too.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Is there another reason I missed which prevents providing this tarball?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
